# App Structure Guide

## Overview
This is a Next.js application for a learning platform with different phases.

## Key Pages
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main entry point / home page
- [app/summary/page.tsx](mdc:app/summary/page.tsx) - Final summary page with learning principles and feedback form

## App Organization
- The application is structured into different phases (phase1 through phase6)
- Each phase represents a step in the learning journey
- The summary page is the final destination for users to provide feedback
- Components are reused across different phases

## Summary Page Details
The summary page displays key learning principles and collects user feedback via quantitative questions on a 1-5 scale. It's designed to be simple and user-friendly.
